# Tell GitHub Linguist to ignore GLAD files for language statistics
# GLAD is a generated OpenGL loader, not part of the actual project code
include/glad/** linguist-vendored
include/KHR/** linguist-vendored
src/glad.c linguist-vendored

# Mark documentation files
*.md linguist-documentation

# Ensure C++ files are properly recognized
*.cpp linguist-language=C++
*.h linguist-language=C++

